1byte=2bit
short: 2byte
int=4byte
long=8byte
float=4byte
double=8byte
char=2byte
boolean=1bit

docker exec -it java-container bash : use whenevr you want to run  java programm 
to execute commands inside container .

docker exec -it java-container javac filename.java
docker exec -it java-container java filename
IF THIS NOT WOKR USE THIS 
docker exec -w /workspace java-container javac FileName.java
docker exec -w /workspace java-container java FileName



How to use GIT

git init # used to initialize repository

git remote add origin <link of github repository> # used to link github repository with gits local repository

git add <filename> # used to add file for tracking

git commit -m "message here" # used to commit changes for tracking

git push -u origin master # used to push changes to github repository

